window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>How do you imprison the world’s most powerful supervillains and make sure they can’t escape?</b></p> <p>The Trench, a supermax prison at the bottom of the deepest part of the Pacific Ocean—toss them in and throw away the key.</p> <p>“Inescapable” doesn’t even begin to describe this place. Even if I could get past the power dampeners and multiple layers of security, where am I going to go?</p> <p>Oh yeah, did I mention I am now the Trench’s newest inmate because I refused to give up being a masked crimefighter? Yeah. Total crap, right?</p> <p>I was captured by the Counter-Vigilante Taskforce, and now the world’s smartest villain—Crosscircuit—wants me to help him with his escape plot.</p> <p>Why would I do that? Let’s just say if I don’t, there’s no way I can handle the consequences.</p> <p>My name is Sawyer William Vincent. Once known as Red Raptor, I'm now Black Harrier, one of the world's most famous masked crime-fighters. At least I used to be…</p> <p><b>The Trench is the second book in the new Harrier series from Audible number one best-selling author Jaime Castle and CJ Valin, the creators of Raptors.</b></p>"; 
